274
00:27:32,996 --> 00:27:35,648
♫  I wish when I wake up  ♫

275
00:27:35,648 --> 00:27:40,300
♫  The morning breeze would sooth my sorrow  ♫

276
00:27:40,300 --> 00:27:42,632
♫  I wish when I turn around  ♫

277
00:27:42,632 --> 00:27:46,824
♫  Everything frosted would melt at my gaze  ♫

278
00:27:47,912 --> 00:27:50,144
♫  I wish when I lift my head  ♫

279
00:27:50,144 --> 00:27:53,668
♫  All I would see is your smiling face  ♫

280
00:27:53,668 --> 00:27:55,344
♫  I wish you would share with me  ♫

281
00:27:55,344 --> 00:27:59,744
♫  Everything you find joyful or troubling  ♫

282
00:28:31,820 --> 00:28:36,400
I've told you many times. 
 Red doesn't suit you.

283
00:28:39,920 --> 00:28:41,560
I like red.

284
00:28:41,560 --> 00:28:47,039
You're still young. 
 You don't know what you truly like.

285
00:28:47,039 --> 00:28:52,159
Do you think I'm too young 
 to know what I like?

286
00:28:52,159 --> 00:28:56,400
Are you talking back to me because of that?

287
00:29:03,900 --> 00:29:07,200
I've only been on a business trip for a few days, 
 and you're already restless.

288
00:29:07,200 --> 00:29:09,700
Why won't you give me peace of mind?

289
00:29:20,320 --> 00:29:22,550
Did you go on a business trip

290
00:29:23,890 --> 00:29:26,480
or visit the cemetery to see my brother?

291
00:29:28,120 --> 00:29:30,660
Whenever I get good grades,

292
00:29:30,660 --> 00:29:34,699
you promptly inform my brother, 
 whom I have never met.

293
00:29:36,540 --> 00:29:39,280
Do you wish for my good grades to be his?

294
00:29:43,400 --> 00:29:48,859
I also wish for him to be your good son.

295
00:29:50,660 --> 00:29:53,080
If you dare leave

296
00:29:58,040 --> 00:30:03,159
I'll go to Lin Hai Feng's house to ask 
 how they educate their daughter.

297
00:30:05,140 --> 00:30:08,999
Meeting a boy late at night?

298
00:30:08,999 --> 00:30:13,340
I want them to know there is a problem 
 with their family's upbringing.

299
00:30:13,340 --> 00:30:15,840
The problem is with our family.

300
00:30:18,739 --> 00:30:22,519
The construction site over in Fujian 
 just happens to be short of engineers.

301
00:30:23,759 --> 00:30:26,320
Let them go where they should go,

302
00:30:26,320 --> 00:30:29,180
and you go where you should go!

303
00:30:29,180 --> 00:30:31,159
Isn't it the perfect solution?

304
00:30:43,200 --> 00:30:45,939
Do you think I'll never grow up?

305
00:30:45,939 --> 00:30:49,299
Do you think you can use such tricks 
 to control me forever?

306
00:30:50,019 --> 00:30:52,900
Of course, I wish you could grow up soon.

307
00:30:53,919 --> 00:30:59,219
Only when you grow up, 
 you'll understand my good intentions.

308
00:31:02,720 --> 00:31:04,380
I'm tired,

309
00:31:05,110 --> 00:31:08,360
and I won't waste more time 
 on these principles.

310
00:31:38,219 --> 00:31:41,280
 Pack your things. 
 I'll take you to the training camp tonight. 

311
00:31:41,280 --> 00:31:42,900
 Don't cause any more trouble. 

312
00:31:42,900 --> 00:31:45,559
 Math is the most important thing now. 

313
00:31:45,559 --> 00:31:48,659
 I'm not going. 
 I want to return to school for classes. 

314
00:31:49,340 --> 00:31:51,319
 Jiang Qiao Xi! 

315
00:31:53,140 --> 00:31:54,940
 I could hear that from outside. 

316
00:31:54,940 --> 00:31:56,759
 Why are you yelling at Qiao Xi? 

317
00:31:56,759 --> 00:31:57,900
 What's wrong again? 

318
00:31:57,900 --> 00:32:00,120
 So what if I did? 

319
00:32:00,120 --> 00:32:03,019
 If it weren't for your promotion 
 and decision to take him to Qunshan, 

320
00:32:03,019 --> 00:32:05,960
 would he have turned out like this? 

321
00:32:05,960 --> 00:32:09,559
 Liang Hong Fei, why are you 
 bringing up old grudges again? 

322
00:32:09,559 --> 00:32:12,859
 Did I not take proper care of the child? 

323
00:32:12,859 --> 00:32:14,330
 When Qiao Xi was little, 

324
00:32:14,330 --> 00:32:17,250
 you didn't like him 
 and refused to care for him. 

325
00:32:17,259 --> 00:32:18,880
 I had work to do. 

326
00:32:18,880 --> 00:32:21,039
 What else could I have done 
 but take him to Qunshan? 

327
00:32:21,039 --> 00:32:23,839
 What do you mean? I also had work to do. 

328
00:32:23,839 --> 00:32:26,800
 So I took him to Qunshan! 

329
00:32:29,216 --> 00:32:33,640
She's smiling. She looks so charming 
 when she smiles.

330
00:32:33,640 --> 00:32:36,860
Put it over here.

331
00:32:36,860 --> 00:32:39,420
Since Qiao Xi transferred schools 
 in fifth grade,

332
00:32:39,420 --> 00:32:42,779
we've rarely seen 
 this kind of smile on Cherry's face.

333
00:32:42,779 --> 00:32:45,739
When she mentioned Qiao Xi tonight,

334
00:32:45,739 --> 00:32:49,920
I felt as if she had returned 
 to her childhood self.

335
00:32:49,920 --> 00:32:53,740
Wait! I thought you wouldn't let her go.

336
00:32:53,740 --> 00:32:55,400
Look at the time!

337
00:32:55,400 --> 00:32:56,660
It's late and she's still not back.

338
00:32:56,660 --> 00:32:58,060
This child, seriously.

339
00:32:58,060 --> 00:33:03,659
Even if you wouldn't let her go, 
 she would find a way.

340
00:33:03,659 --> 00:33:07,159
Besides, if something is troubling her,

341
00:33:07,159 --> 00:33:10,380
she wouldn't tell us.

342
00:33:10,380 --> 00:33:16,759
Friendships at that age are the purest 
 and deserve the best protection.

343
00:33:16,759 --> 00:33:18,360
Yes.

344
00:33:23,060 --> 00:33:26,019
Who is it? It's so late.

345
00:33:29,559 --> 00:33:31,900
Mr. Cai?

346
00:33:31,900 --> 00:33:34,819
Manager Cai, it's late. What's going on?

347
00:33:34,819 --> 00:33:37,519
 Mr. Lin, Ms. Liang and Mr. Jiang 
 are fighting at home. 

348
00:33:37,519 --> 00:33:39,279
 The cadre building is in turmoil. 

349
00:33:39,279 --> 00:33:42,912
 It appears the cause is Cherry and Qiao Xi. 

350
00:33:42,912 --> 00:33:44,140
What?

351
00:33:44,140 --> 00:33:46,980
 You've been a father twice. 
 When were you ever competent? 

352
00:33:46,980 --> 00:33:49,380
 Do you want to ruin both your children? 

353
00:33:49,380 --> 00:33:51,420
 This happened more than a decade ago. 

354
00:33:51,420 --> 00:33:53,600
 You've been clinging to it! 
 What exactly do you want? 

355
00:33:53,600 --> 00:33:54,839
 What do I want? 

356
00:33:54,839 --> 00:33:56,099
 Tell me! What do you want? 

357
00:33:56,099 --> 00:33:59,840
 You've always used this 
 to torture and blame me. 

358
00:33:59,840 --> 00:34:01,339
 Do you want my life? 

359
00:34:01,339 --> 00:34:03,339
 Take it for Meng Chu! 

360
00:34:03,339 --> 00:34:05,200
 - Then this matter will be over!  
 - Aunt Juan.

361
00:34:05,200 --> 00:34:07,759
 No one in this world 
 can compensate for my son's life! 

362
00:34:07,759 --> 00:34:09,840
 Can you discipline Jiang Qiao Xi? 

363
00:34:09,840 --> 00:34:13,980
 Lin Hai Feng's daughter asked your son 
 to meet her at night! 

364
00:34:13,980 --> 00:34:15,340
 If you really consider yourself a father, 

365
00:34:15,340 --> 00:34:17,739
 go to the Lin family and tell them 

366
00:34:17,739 --> 00:34:20,079
 to urge their daughter 
 to stay away from Jiang Qiao Xi! 

367
00:34:20,079 --> 00:34:21,880
 If you want to go crazy, go ahead! 

368
00:34:21,880 --> 00:34:24,019
 No one will join you! 

369
00:34:38,084 --> 00:34:41,444
♫  Even if we stumble  ♫ 
 ♫  We will always be strong  ♫

370
00:34:41,444 --> 00:34:44,032
♫  Count the falling stars  ♫ 
 ♫  That land on your shoulder  ♫

371
00:34:44,032 --> 00:34:49,152
♫  I will always be by your side  ♫

372
00:34:49,152 --> 00:34:52,320
♫  Life should always chase the light  ♫

373
00:34:52,320 --> 00:34:54,208
♫  Once we get through despair  ♫ 
 ♫  We can embrace even more hope  ♫

374
00:34:57,039 --> 00:34:59,579
Why are you here?

375
00:34:59,579 --> 00:35:03,800
I-I was just passing by,

376
00:35:03,800 --> 00:35:07,619
and I saw you here alone.

377
00:35:07,619 --> 00:35:09,760
Jiang Qiao Xi hasn't come yet.

378
00:35:09,760 --> 00:35:11,760
Did you tell him the time?

379
00:35:11,760 --> 00:35:13,979
I told him!

380
00:35:15,260 --> 00:35:17,860
It's so late, yet he still hasn't come over.

381
00:35:17,860 --> 00:35:23,400
Why don't we go home now?

382
00:35:23,400 --> 00:35:25,839
Let's go! I'll walk you back.

383
00:35:56,004 --> 00:35:58,700
Qiao Xi, I'm sorry.

384
00:35:58,700 --> 00:36:00,559
I'm to blame today.

385
00:36:00,559 --> 00:36:02,959
I was the one who asked Cherry out.

386
00:36:04,280 --> 00:36:08,360
I had something to tell her, 
 but I can't go now.

387
00:36:08,360 --> 00:36:10,579
Could you please apologize to her 
 on my behalf?

388
00:36:10,579 --> 00:36:12,739
Jiang Qiao Xi!

389
00:36:12,739 --> 00:36:16,940
I have to attend 
 the Math Olympiad training camp now.

390
00:36:16,940 --> 00:36:20,099
Mr. Lin, Sheng Juan.

391
00:36:20,099 --> 00:36:22,320
They are going to the same school,

392
00:36:22,320 --> 00:36:25,559
so it's normal for them to interact.

393
00:36:26,680 --> 00:36:29,888
It's so late. I am sorry you had to come here 
 over our family matter.

394
00:36:29,888 --> 00:36:30,900
I'm really sorry.

395
00:36:30,900 --> 00:36:33,579
Is this just our family matter?

396
00:36:38,519 --> 00:36:42,360
Mom! Let's go now.

397
00:36:42,360 --> 00:36:47,419
I will definitely… keep my promise to you.

398
00:36:48,480 --> 00:36:50,860
I'll trust you one last time.

399
00:37:07,460 --> 00:37:08,976
Cherry!

400
00:37:11,780 --> 00:37:12,840
Cherry! Cherry!

401
00:37:12,840 --> 00:37:15,979
Cherry, don't go!

402
00:37:15,979 --> 00:37:17,800
Cherry!

403
00:37:34,219 --> 00:37:35,900
Mom!

404
00:37:35,900 --> 00:37:37,999
Aunt Juan, Uncle Hai Feng.

405
00:37:37,999 --> 00:37:41,459
Cherry didn't do anything wrong. 
 She didn't.

406
00:37:44,072 --> 00:37:45,760
Thank you.

407
00:37:45,760 --> 00:37:51,360
Yu Qiao, it's late. Go back.

408
00:37:51,360 --> 00:37:53,460
You should go back now.

409
00:38:03,119 --> 00:38:06,959
I'm sorry, I…

410
00:38:06,959 --> 00:38:11,019
All right, don't worry.

411
00:38:11,019 --> 00:38:14,059
We don't think you were at fault.

412
00:38:16,579 --> 00:38:18,164
Let's go back.

413
00:38:20,059 --> 00:38:21,479
Let's go.

414
00:38:21,479 --> 00:38:23,839
Let's go back.

415
00:38:29,900 --> 00:38:33,220
It's getting cooler now.

416
00:38:33,220 --> 00:38:35,064
It's autumn now.

417
00:38:36,059 --> 00:38:40,539
I'll make some rock sugar pear water for you 
 to take to school. All right?

418
00:38:42,939 --> 00:38:44,620
Mom…

419
00:38:45,660 --> 00:38:50,080
did Jiang Qiao Xi's mom 
 say anything unpleasant to you?

420
00:38:51,360 --> 00:38:55,019
Cherry, don't forget who I am.

421
00:38:55,019 --> 00:38:57,600
I'm an ace electrician!

422
00:38:58,880 --> 00:39:01,619
No matter how high 
 Qiao Xi's mother's position is,

423
00:39:01,619 --> 00:39:07,679
she should still be polite to me. 
 Isn't that right?

424
00:39:08,300 --> 00:39:12,360
I've caused you trouble again!

425
00:39:12,360 --> 00:39:15,300
When you get older and become a parent,

426
00:39:15,300 --> 00:39:20,900
you'll understand 
 children grow up among troubles.

427
00:39:34,980 --> 00:39:36,550
Well…

428
00:39:37,370 --> 00:39:42,120
Well, is Jiang Qiao Xi all right?

429
00:39:43,660 --> 00:39:47,420
Cherry, is a good boy.

430
00:39:47,420 --> 00:39:51,500
He cares about your friendship, 
 just as much as you do,

431
00:39:51,500 --> 00:39:56,039
but many times, especially at your age,

432
00:39:56,039 --> 00:39:58,479
it's difficult to change a given situation,

433
00:39:58,479 --> 00:40:00,979
and rely on yourself to make decisions.

434
00:40:42,860 --> 00:40:48,639
Although often, 
 people cannot change their situation,

435
00:40:49,679 --> 00:40:57,120
friendship is something 
 circumstances can't change. Isn't that so?

436
00:40:59,499 --> 00:41:01,204
Of course!

437
00:41:10,360 --> 00:41:12,052
Let's go!

438
00:41:37,700 --> 00:41:45,276
   

439
00:41:45,276 --> 00:41:47,219
Yun Yun.

440
00:41:47,219 --> 00:41:48,800
Uncle Jiang.

441
00:41:48,800 --> 00:41:50,979
Give me a pack of cigarettes.

442
00:42:04,900 --> 00:42:07,619
Do you need anything else?

443
00:42:20,619 --> 00:42:22,190
Yun Yun,

444
00:42:23,740 --> 00:42:27,160
you are close to Cherry.

445
00:42:27,160 --> 00:42:30,919
Can you talk to her?

446
00:42:31,840 --> 00:42:37,280
At your current stage, 
 the most important thing is studying.

447
00:42:39,720 --> 00:42:44,960
Besides that, it's important 
to establish healthy interpersonal relationships,

448
00:42:45,900 --> 00:42:48,579
including friendships

449
00:42:48,579 --> 00:42:53,019
and potential romantic relationships, 
 in the future.

450
00:42:54,599 --> 00:42:57,720
All this should happen at the right time.

451
00:42:57,720 --> 00:43:02,579
At this stage, it's best 
 not to influence each other.

452
00:43:04,219 --> 00:43:10,460
Mr. Jiang, if there's any influence, 
 it's Jiang Qiao Xi who is influencing Cherry.

